      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This fantastic vehicle is in good condition and ready for its next owner! It has been well-maintained and drives beautifully, offering a dependable performance you can count on. While it shows some light, expected wear from careful use, it remains a clean and impressive choice for anyone seeking quality and value. Don't miss out on this great find!",
